== 对等连接 ==
Cogent在ISP市场中的低带宽定价及与[[美国在线|AOL]]（2003）、<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://legalminds.lp.findlaw.com/list/cyberia-l/msg42080.html|title='Peering' Dispute With AOL Slows Cogent Customer Access|last=Noguchi|first=Yuki|date=2002-12-27|publisher=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|accessdate=2006-09-28|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120714085429/http://legalminds.lp.findlaw.com/list/cyberia-l/msg42080.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[Orange_(公司)|France Telecom]]（2006）、<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://morse.colorado.edu/~epperson/courses/routing-protocols/handouts/cogent-ft.html|title=France Telecom severs all network links to competitor Cogent|last=Kuri|first=Jürgen|date=2005-04-21|publisher=[[Heinz_Heise|Heise online]]|last2=Smith, Robert W.|accessdate=2006-09-28|archive-date=2006-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060908103607/http://morse.colorado.edu/~epperson/courses/routing-protocols/handouts/cogent-ft.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[Level_3_通信|Level 3 Communications]]（2005）、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&STORY=%2Fwww%2Fstory%2F10-07-2005%2F0004163871&EDATE |title=Cogent Press release Level3 dispute Oct 7 2005 |access-date=2020-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930180734/http://www2.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&STORY=%2Fwww%2Fstory%2F10-07-2005%2F0004163871&EDATE |archive-date=2012-09-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> [[TeliaSonera|TeliaSonera]]（2008年3月）<ref name="giga-malik">[http://gigaom.com/2008/03/14/the-telia-cogent-spat-could-ruin-web-for-many/ The Telia-Cogent Spat Could Ruin the Web For Many] {{Wayback|url=http://gigaom.com/2008/03/14/the-telia-cogent-spat-could-ruin-web-for-many/ |date=20161227065732 }}, Om Malik, 2008-03-14</ref>和[[Sprint|Sprint Nextel]]（2008年10月）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.earthtimes.org/articles/show/sprint-nextel-severs-its-internet-connection-to-cogent-communications,603138.shtml |title=Sprint-Nextel Severs Its Internet Connection to Cogent Communications |accessdate=2017-02-12 |archive-date=2016-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012182440/http://www.earthtimes.org/articles/show/sprint-nextel-severs-its-internet-connection-to-cogent-communications,603138.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>的{{tsl|en|Peering|对等连接}}一直存在争议。

2008年3月14日，Cogent停止路由来自欧洲网络提供商[[TeliaSonera|Telia]]（[[自治系统|AS]] 1299）的数据包，这两个网络之间失去连通性。该连接在2008年3月28日重新建立，在美国和欧洲设有互连点。<ref>[http://thelocal.se/10786/20080330/ Telia resolves internet dispute] {{Wayback|url=http://thelocal.se/10786/20080330/ |date=20080607080053 }}, http://thelocal.se {{Wayback|url=http://thelocal.se/ |date=20170213011129 }}, Peter Vinthagen Simpson, 2008-03-30</ref>

2011年6月6日，Cogent自动停止与[[能源科学网|能源科学网]]（ESnet）的对等连接<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110611002310/http://es.net/news-and-publications/important-status-regarding-cogent-connectivity/ Important: Status regarding Cogent connectivity], Energy Sciences Network press release, Steve Cotter, Lawrence Berkeley National Lab</ref>，导致3天的中断。

Cogent尚未同意与最大的IPv6连接提供商[[Hurricane_Electric|Hurricane Electric]]对等连接。截至2016年3月，不能在两个网络之间直接连接。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mailman.nanog.org/pipermail/nanog/2009-October/014017.html |title=E-mail from Hurricane Electric explaining why the two networks are severed on the nanog (North American Network Operators Group) mailing list |accessdate=2017-02-12 |archive-date=2009-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091016011024/https://mailman.nanog.org/pipermail/nanog/2009-October/014017.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>Cogent与[[Google|Google]]的IPv6对等连接也已在2016年停止。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://adminhacks.com/broken-IPv6.html |title=adminhacks.org, March 2016 |accessdate=2017-02-12 |archive-date=2016-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314022104/http://adminhacks.com/broken-IPv6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年2月，Cogent屏蔽众多[[盗版|盗版]]和[[流媒体|流媒体]]网站，包括[[海盜灣|海盜灣]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://torrentfreak.com/internet-backbone-provider-cogent-blocks-pirate-bay-and-other-pirate-sites-170209/|title=Internet Backbone Provider Cogent Blocks Pirate Bay and other "Pirate" Sites - TorrentFreak|date=9 February 2017|work=TorrentFreak|accessdate=2017-02-12|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211225311/https://torrentfreak.com/internet-backbone-provider-cogent-blocks-pirate-bay-and-other-pirate-sites-170209/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

